snippet.textDisplay:
Iz*One, Cherry Bullet, EverGlow and Rocket Punch first conversation in ages since produce:

Suyun: Hi power vocal gurl.
Haeyoon: Hi cutie pie, you should talk. You've been hiding that vocal during produce all that time?
Yiren: Don't forget about me, i got the killer parts in the chorus.
Sohee: I'm so envious of you, you got so sexy this era. Thank god we keep getting comebacks.
Chaeyeon and Nako: I know right. We are so happy to be back pretty ladies.
Juri: Oh my god, did you guys remember? We were on the Top 20 back then.
Sihyeon: I'm pissed though, it was my second time and haven't gotten as lucky as you guys. 
Suyun: Babe, it was rigged, no worries.
Hitomi and Sakura: We are not involved, AKS are not involved in that.
Yena: So did Yuehua.
Minju: Well, Urban Works didn't have any connections. They just send me in and i fight alone. 
Haeyoon, Sohee and Yiren: So who was?
Eunbi, Hyewon, Wonyoung and Yuri: …
Chaewon: Strangely, i never even made to the Top 12 until the finals.
Gowon: Guys, you should know, i almost audition for produce, to follow Yujin. She eventually left BlockBerry.
Alexa: It's okay though. I struggle for my debut but at least my company didn't do anything horrible.
Doah: Well, my groups debut didn’t do well at all.
Hyunah: Well, I fully left the industry. Too many chaos and companies are just terrible at making business decisions.
Gaeun: Thank god Pledis didn’t do that as well. In fact, they were pissed so they didn’t manage the group afterwards because they had suspect something wrong.
Eunyoung: Well, they didn’t pick me. They picked another girl from my company, and it wasn’t Gyuri.
Doyeon: My season was the best bitches, only a few minor changes.
Umji: Join Source Music. We didn’t do that even in Produce X, our trainees got treated heavily bad.
Stone Music: took izone back to the dressing room and never talk to the other girls again

Looking forward for Haeyoon, Juri, Sihyeon, Sohee, Suyun, Yiren and these twelve girls interacting. Haeyoon and Juri were with them during Top 20, while Sihyeon and Yiren missed and only got to Top 30. I wish Alexa and Doah did a comeback as well, while Eunyoung, Jinny, Minseo, Sian and whoever else can get together as well. They could maybe... talk about the controversy, and whether or not they knew about it or i dunno...
